          <p>By showing this QR code you will gain exclusive access to the hall to attend the ceremony, simply show your invite to the hall personnel before entering.</p>
        <% } else if(faction == 1001) {%>
          <p>By showing this QR code you will gain access to the hall until all available seats are reserved. To enter, show this invite to the hall personnel.</p>
